    "text": "Published as a conference paper at ICLR 2026\nUNIFIED ANALYSES FOR HIERARCHICAL FEDERATED\nLEARNING:\nTOPOLOGY SELECTION\nUNDER DATA\nHETEROGENEITY\nZiyi Zhou1, Yipeng Li2 & Xinchen Lyu1‚àó\n1National Engineering Research Center for Mobile Network Technologies,\nBeijing University of Posts and Telecommunications\n2Tsinghua Shenzhen International Graduate School, Tsinghua University\n{zhouzy0821, lvxinchen}@bupt.edu.cn, liyp25@mails.tsinghua.edu.cn\nABSTRACT",
