    "text": "Published as a conference paper at ICLR 2026\ndata heterogeneity (Wang et al., 2022), partial client participation (Jiang & Zhu, 2024), and other\nvariants (Liu et al., 2022; Yang et al., 2023). Some recent works explore Star-Ring topology (Chen\net al., 2020; Lee et al., 2020; Fang et al., 2022; Ding et al., 2024) and the Ring-Star topology\n(Chaoyang et al., 2020; Huang et al., 2024; Yan et al., 2025). However, a unified convergence",
