    "text": "s limited by\nthe straggler, i.e., T Star = maxm{\nS\nr0‚Üím + œÑm +\nSs limited by\nthe straggler, i.e., T Star = maxm{\nS\nr0‚Üím + œÑm +\nSrm‚Üí0 }, where the index 0 denotes the aggregation\nserver. Conversely, the Ring topology operates sequentially, accumulating latencies: T Ring =\nS\nr0‚Üí1 +\n14",
    "source": "iclr_2026.pdf",
