    "text": "‚Ä≤=0\n1\nM 2\nM\nX\nm‚Ä≤=1\nK‚àí1\nX\nk‚Ä≤=0\nE‚à•‚àáF(x)‚à•2 + gPMK\ng‚àí1\nX\ng‚Ä≤=1\nP ‚àí1\nX‚Ä≤=0\n1\nM 2\nM\nX\nm‚Ä≤=1\nK‚àí1\nX\nk‚Ä≤=0\nE‚à•‚àáF(x)‚à•2 + gPMK\ng‚àí1\nX\ng‚Ä≤=1\nP ‚àí1\nXp‚Ä≤=0\n1\nM 2\nM\nX\nm‚Ä≤=1\nK‚àí1\nX\nk‚Ä≤=0\nE‚à•‚àáF(x)‚à•2\n!\n‚â§15Œ∑2GPMK2œÉ2 + 15Œ∑2GP 2K2œÉ2 + 15Œ∑2G2P 2K2œÉ2\n+ 15Œ∑2GPMK3Œ∂2 + 15Œ∑2GPMK3Œ¥2 + 15Œ∑2GP 3MK3Œ¥2 + 15Œ∑2G3P 3MK3Œ¥2\n+ 15Œ∑2GPMK3‚à•‚àáF (x)‚à•2 + 15Œ∑2GP 3MK3‚à•‚àáF (x)‚à•2 + 15Œ∑2G3P 3MK3‚à•‚àáF (x)‚à•2\n+ 15L2G2P 2K2Œ∑2Er\nLet c1 =\n1\n1‚àí15L2G2P 2K2Œ∑2 , we have\nEr ‚â§15c1Œ∑2GPMK2œÉ2 + 30c1Œ∑2G2P 2K2œÉ2 + 15c1Œ∑2GPMK3Œ∂2 + 45c1Œ∑2G3P 3MK3Œ¥2\n+ 45c1Œ∑2G3P 3MK3‚à•‚àáF (x)‚à•2\nAfter substituting Er into E[F(x(r+1)) ‚àíF(x(r))], we can obtain\nE[F(x(r+1)) ‚àíF(x(r))]\n‚â§‚àíŒ∑GPK(1\n2 ‚àí45\n2 c1Œ∑2L2G2P 2K2)E[‚à•‚àáF(x(r))‚à•2] + Œ∑2LGPK\nM",
